sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval<br/>Operator
    participant Pod as Job Pod<br/>(lm-evaluation-harness)
    participant JobSpec as /meta/job.json<br/>(ConfigMap)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Endpoint<br/>(vLLM/TGI/OpenAI)<br/>Configurable Port
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>Configurable Port

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Operator,Pod: Flow 1: Online Evaluation Job Execution
        Operator->>Pod: Create Pod (mount job.json,<br/>secrets, volumes)
        Pod->>JobSpec: Read job spec<br/>(filesystem read)
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Bearer Token
        Pod->>HF: GET tokenizer files<br/>HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HF-->>Pod: AutoTokenizer artifacts
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Bearer Token
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>Bearer Token

        loop For each evaluation prompt (num_concurrent <= 128)
            Pod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>OPENAI_API_KEY Bearer Token
            Model-->>Pod: Completion response
        end

        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Bearer Token
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Bearer Token
        Pod->>OCI: Push OCI artifact<br/>(via skopeo)<br/>Registry credentials
        OCI-->>Pod: Push confirmation
        Pod->>MLflow: Log experiment metrics<br/>(optional, via evalhub SDK)
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST results + status: COMPLETE<br/>Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Operator,Model: Flow 2: Offline / Air-Gapped Evaluation
        Operator->>Pod: Create Pod (mount /test_data PVC,<br/>job.json, secrets)
        Pod->>JobSpec: Read job spec
        Note over Pod: Auto-detect /test_data:<br/>tokenizer + dataset_dict.json<br/>Set HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Bearer Token
        Note over Pod: Load tokenizer from<br/>/test_data (local)
        Note over Pod: Load datasets from<br/>/test_data (local)
        Note over Pod: Load metrics from<br/>metrics/ directory (local)
        Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION

        loop For each evaluation prompt
            Pod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>(internal cluster endpoint)<br/>Custom CA support
            Model-->>Pod: Completion response
        end

        Pod->>EvalHub: POST results + status: COMPLETE
    end
